1:1 COMMENT "# tagaccessor.z - Explicit read-only tag accessor"
1:50 EOL "\n"
2:1 COMMENT "#"
2:2 EOL "\n"
3:1 COMMENT "# A variant/union as-item of the form `name: <numeric>.tag` exposes the"
3:72 EOL "\n"
4:1 COMMENT "# discriminator on instances: `x.name` reads the current arm's ordinal"
4:71 EOL "\n"
5:1 COMMENT "# (declaration order, starting at 0) as the declared numeric type. It is"
5:73 EOL "\n"
6:1 COMMENT "# read-only, and without such a declaration the tag is not exposed."
6:68 EOL "\n"
7:1 COMMENT "# bool declares `tag: u8.tag` in the system unit, so `b.tag` reads 0/1."
7:72 EOL "\n"
8:1 EOL "\n"
